---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome to Serbia Shop!</h1>
			<p>
				Your premier destination for relocating to Serbia. We provide the essential resources, 
        hand-picked local products, and expert immigration insights you need to make your 
        transition to Serbia seamless and successful.
			</p>
			<p>
				Whether you are seeking residency, looking for authentic Serbian craftsmanship, 
        or simply exploring the rich culture of the Balkans, our blog and shop are here 
        to guide you every step of the way.
			</p>
			<p>How we can help you:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Business Formation:</strong> Full support for registering a limited liability company (DOO) or entrepreneur status (Preduzetnik).</li>
        <li><strong>Residency Applications:</strong> Expertise in residency based on business ownership, employment, or family reunification.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal & Tax Consultation:</strong> Guidance on local tax obligations and banking for new international residents.</li>
        <li><strong>Administrative Handling:</strong> We manage your translations, notary appointments, and all interactions with the Ministry of Interior.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Stay tuned as we continue to add new resources and products daily. Serbia is waiting for you! <a href="https://docs.astro.build/"
					>read the docs
				</a> or <a href="https://astro.build/chat">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
			</p>
			<p>
				Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a
					href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template"
					>astro-blog-template
				</a> by <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
